  <div class="container-width py-16">
    <p class="eyebrow">Security posture</p>
    <h2 class="section-title mt-3">Current mail security controls</h2>
    <div class="card mt-6">
      <p class="text-muted">
        Domain registration is managed on
        <a
          class="text-text underline decoration-accent/60 underline-offset-2"
